creator: Frances Ridley Havergal
description: LibriVox volunteers bring you 9 recordings of Most Blessed For Ever by Frances Ridley Havergal. This was the Weekly Poetry project for January 11, 2015. Read in English by Adele de Pignerolles; Ann Boulais; Bruce Kachuk; David Lawrence; Esther ben Simonides; Greg Giordano; Lee Ann Howlett; Larry Wilsonand Leonard Wilson. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. Download M4B (5MB)
